oks at superficial things like the physical body they came in, and tries to fit them in some pattern, one will only draw superficial conclusions.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;yiv1276886991yui_3_7_2_37_1367796055441_96 yiv1276886991yui_3_7_2_27_1368126251839_110&quot; style=&quot;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size:13.3333px;font-family:arial, helvetica, sans-serif;background-color:transparent;font-style:normal;&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;yiv1276886991yui_3_7_2_37_1367796055441_97 yiv1276886991yui_3_7_2_27_1368126251839_111&quot; style=&quot;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size:13px;font-family:arial, helvetica, clean,\n sans-serif;background-color:transparent;font-style:normal;&quot;&gt;Best\n regards,&lt;br&gt;Narasimha&lt;br&gt;--------&lt;br&gt;Astrology &amp; Spirituality Resources: &lt;a rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; href=&quot;http://www.vedicastrologer.org/&quot;&gt;http://www.VedicAstrologer.org&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;yiv1276886991yui_3_7_2_37_1367796055441_98 yiv1276886991yui_3_7_2_27_1368126251839_112&quot; style=&quot;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size:13px;font-family:arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif;background-color:transparent;font-style:normal;&quot;&gt;--------&lt;br&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;blockquote style=&quot;border-left:2px solid rgb(16, 16, 255);&quot;&gt;  &lt;div class=&quot;yiv1276886991yui_3_7_2_37_1367796055441_100 yiv1276886991yui_3_7_2_27_1368126251839_114&quot; style=&quot;font-family:arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:10pt;&quot;&gt; &lt;div class=&quot;yiv1276886991yui_3_7_2_37_1367796055441_101 yiv1276886991yui_3_7_2_27_1368126251839_115&quot; style=&quot;font-family:times new roman, new york, times, serif;font-size:12pt;&quot;&gt; &lt;div dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt; &lt;hr size=&quot;1&quot;&gt;  &lt;font face=&quot;Arial&quot; size=&quot;2&quot;&gt; &lt;b&gt;&lt;span\n style=&quot;font-weight:bold;&quot;&gt;From:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt; rajarshi 